    <item>
      <title>被遗忘的中英股票互联互通计划现在需要重启</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-29/the-forgotten-uk-china-stock-connect-program-now-needs-a-reboot</link>
      <description><![CDATA[多年来，伦敦证券交易所一直宣称与中国股市建立联系将使全球投资者能够通过英国参与亚洲国家的增长。然而，自该机制推出近五年以来，它已淡出了人们的视线。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-29/the-forgotten-uk-china-stock-connect-program-now-needs-a-reboot</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 29 May 2024 06:40:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
